releaseNotes:
In this new version:
- Introduction of DBBrokerLive (Runtime resolution of result sets);
- Security improvement with the introduction of Encryption Password to DBBroker.config file;
- Complete documentation of the library;
- Fix of the class SqlScriptMaker that now can be executed on dynamic assemblies;

Special thanks to the great contribution of:
Giovanni Barros (PGE/RN)
Ionaldo Carvalho Júnior (PGE/RN)
Laerte Bacatela (SEEC/RN)

Their help announcing this tool for technical and academic public is really valuable. Great feedback and contributions are already coming.
